  "title": "🌟 Junior Growth Associate (b2b, ASAP, office hours!))",
  "description": "<p><u><strong> Junior B2B Growth Associate (ASAP!)</strong></u><br />Entry-Level | Office Hours | No Experience Needed</p><p>As a Junior B2B Growth Associate, you’ll work closely with our corporate clients, learn how businesses operate, and help drive meaningful partnerships — all while being coached by experienced mentors.</p><p>No experience? No problem. We provide full training, hands-on guidance, and a supportive team environment to help you grow confidently.</p><p><u> What You’ll Do:</u></p><ul><li>Assist in developing and expanding B2B customer relationships</li><li>Present campaigns and solutions to potential business</li><li>Support outreach, meetings, and follow-up with companies</li><li>Work with the team to hit growth and sales targets</li><li>Gain real experience in communication, negotiation & corporate sales</li></ul><p><u> What You’ll Get:</u></p><ul><li>Office hours </li><li>1-on-1 mentorship and on-job training</li><li>Clear career progression into management roles</li><li>Fun, supportive and growth-focused team culture</li><li>Fresh grads / ORD welcome — learn everything on the job!</li></ul><p><u> Who We’re Looking For:</u></p><ul><li>Outgoing, driven, and eager to learn</li><li>Enjoys meeting new people and building meaningful connections</li><li>Motivated by results and personal development</li><li>Ready to start on short notice</li></ul><p><em><strong> Apply now and jumpstart your career with us!</strong></em></p>",
